oh well first of all at top of scren on the mopar client it says help. u click it then hit item ids. then click help again and hit command list. well type in the item u want on ids then type
::pickup (id of item here) (amount wanted here). its all in the commands. now also the first code is unnoted and the one under it is noted. enjoy
